Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.25,0:24:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.33,0:24:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些 为明天而奋斗的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.55,0:24:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请握住我的手
